data.description: Beautiful 2 bedroom with possible 3rd bedroom/den/study/office, 2.5 bathroom townhome in Village on the Green.    This landominium is conveniently located between Loveland and Morrow in Hamilton Township.  It is close to shopping (a new super-Kroger is being built), restaurants and entertainment  The home features a 2-car garage with direct entry into the unit, a two-story great room, master bedroom with an en-suite bath, and large walk-in closet.  A third room could be used as a bedroom, office or study.  It also features a first-floor laundry, eat-in kitchen, separate dining area and living room with a walk-out to a deck with a wooded view in the back.   Village on the Green offers nice amenities, including a pool, tennis courts, play area, fishing lakes and walking path.
